{
  "stem": "8916.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my argument to this-- to this Nazi officer who would shoot a Jew at-- for nothing, I was explaining to him that I was not allowed out, and that my mother is in a group and she is leaving and my brother and my father are already there.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was my argument.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Pretty naive little boy of 13 talking to this nasty looking German officer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I could just about-- my eye-- my eye level was just about even with his belt.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he looked at his assistant and asked him if that was true.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the assistant said yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He saw my name on the list.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he ordered me into this group, and I made it out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But while I was doing-- while I was in the group waiting to leave, I looked over and there was the assistant trying to talk to this officer about something about this incident.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was trying to explain to him why I couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he refused to listen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He even got mad at his assistant for-- you know, for arguing with him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In any case, I'd like to think that it would be nice to know that maybe for an instant this-- this Nazi, foggy, brained Nazi German who accepted Nazi philosophy that some people are less than human and they can be shot at will probably saw a little boy--",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and decided that this was the natural thing for a little boy to do is to go where his parents are.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I never accepted that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they had a place at the very beginning of this camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had barracks just for-- for children about my age.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I wouldn't go near those places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wouldn't go near those barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
